de\": {\"-p\", \"--output-format\", \"stream-json\", \"--verbose\", \"--dangerously-skip-permissions\"},\n}\n```\n\n**Agent Configuration Hierarchy** (resolution order):\n1. Step-level: `agent_command` and `agent_args` in step config\n2. Workflow-level: `container.agent_command` and `container.agent_args` (container workflows) or `host.agent_command` and `host.agent_args` (host workflows)\n3. Environment variable: `CLOCHE_AGENT_COMMAND`\n4. Default: `\"claude\"`\n\n**Container Workflow Agent Resolution** (`/workspace/internal/agent/runner.go`, lines 55-63):\n```go\nif cmd, ok := os.LookupEnv(\"CLOCHE_AGENT_COMMAND\"); ok {\n    promptAdapter.Commands = prompt.ParseCommands(cmd)\n}\nif cmd := wf.Config[\"container.agent_command\"]; cmd != \"\" {\n    promptAdapter.Commands = prompt.ParseCommands(cmd)\n}\nif args := wf.Config[\"container.agent_args\"]; args != \"\" {\n    promptAdapter.ExplicitArgs = strings.Fields(args)\n}\n```\n\n**Host Workflow Agent Resolution** (`/workspace/internal/host/executor.go`, lines 225-242):\n```go\nadapter := prompt.New()\n\n// Apply workflow-level agent config\nif len(e.AgentCommands) > 0 {\n    adapter.Commands = e.AgentCommands\n}\nif len(e.AgentArgs) > 0 {\n    adapter.ExplicitArgs = e.AgentArgs\n}\n\n// Step-level overrides\nif cmd := step.Config[\"agent_command\"]; cmd != \"\" {\n    adapter.Commands = prompt.ParseCommands(cmd)\n}\nif args := step.Config[\"agent_args\"]; args != \"\" {\n    adapter.ExplicitArgs = strings.Fields(args)\n}\n```\n\n**ParseCommands Function** (`/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go`, lines 55-67):\nSplits comma-separated agent_command string: `\"claude,gemini\"` → `[\"claude\", \"gemini\"]`\n\n### 5. **Known Step Config Keys**\n\n(`/workspace/internal/domain/workflow.go`, lines 246-257):\n```go\nvar knownStepConfigKeys = map[string]bool{\n    \"prompt\":        true,\n    \"run\":           true,\n    \"max_attempts\":  true,\n    \"timeout\":       true,\n    \"agent_command\": true,     // step-level override\n    \"agent_args\":    true,     // step-level override\n    \"results\":       true,\n    \"feedback\":      true,     // include previous step feedback\n    \"workflow_name\": true,\n    \"prompt_step\":   true,     // override source for prompt content\n}\n```\n\n### 6. **Test Files**\n\n**DSL Parser Tests** (`/workspace/internal/dsl/parser_test.go`):\n- Full workflow parsing\n- Minimal workflows\n- Container blocks at workflow and step level\n- Host block location detection\n- Output path expressions\n- Collect conditions (all/any)\n- Conflict detection between host/container blocks\n\n**Prompt Adapter Tests** (`/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt_test.go`):\n- Command execution with feedback\n- Max attempts limiting\n- Fallback chain handling (command not found, non-zero exit without marker)\n- Result marker detection (CLOCHE_RESULT:success/fail)\n- Output file writing\n- Attempt count tracking\n- `ParseCommands()` function tests\n\n**Domain Validation Tests** (`/workspace/internal/domain/workflow_test.go`):\n- Step type inference\n- Wiring validation\n- Unreachable step detection\n- Duplicate result mapping detection\n- Output path evaluation\n\n### 7. **File Locations**\n\n**Core DSL:**\n- `/workspace/internal/dsl/lexer.go` - Lexical analysis\n- `/workspace/internal/dsl/token.go` - Token definitions\n- `/workspace/internal/dsl/parser.go` - Parser implementation\n- `/workspace/internal/domain/workflow.go` - Domain types and validation\n\n**Agent Adapters:**\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go` - Prompt agent implementation\n- `/workspace/internal/adapters/agents/generic/generic.go` - Script/run adapter\n- `/workspace/internal/ports/agent.go` - AgentAdapter interface\n\n**Execution:**\n- `/workspace/internal/agent/runner.go` - Container workflow execution\n- `/workspace/internal/host/executor.go` - Host workflow execution\n- `/workspace/internal/engine/` - Workflow graph traversal engine\n\n**Documentation:**\n- `/workspace/docs/workflows.md` - Complete DSL syntax and semantics\n- `/workspace/CLAUDE.md` - Project overview and architecture\n\n### 8. **Key Type Definitions Summary**\n\n| Type | Location | Purpose |\n|------|----------|---------|\n| `Step` | domain/workflow.go:35 | Single workflow step definition |\n| `Workflow` | domain/workflow.go:135 | Complete workflow graph |\n| `Wire` | domain/workflow.go:42 | Step→step result routing |\n| `OutputPath` | domain/workflow.go:62 | JSON path expressions |\n| `Adapter` (prompt) | adapters/agents/prompt/prompt.go:25 | Agent execution wrapper |\n| `Parser` | dsl/parser.go:11 | DSL parser state machine |\n| `Lexer` | dsl/lexer.go:3 | Token stream generator |\n| `StepType` | domain/workflow.go:14 | Enum: agent/script/workflow |\n| `WorkflowLocation` | domain/workflow.go:23 | Enum: container/host |"}],"totalDurationMs":47509,"totalTokens":60715,"totalToolUseCount":26,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":921,"cache_read_input_tokens":56967,"output_tokens":2823,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":921},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
